headline: 2 Dirt Cheap AI Stocks to Buy in June
summary: Alphabet and Adobe are both cheaper than the broader market.  "Dirt cheap" and artificial intelligence (AI) aren't typically mentioned in the same sentence.  Two of them are Alphabet (NASDAQ: GOOG) (NASDAQ: GOOGL) and Adobe (NASDAQ: ADBE), and each looks like an incredible buy right now.
